					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Personally I don't see the point of using a hardware RNG. The RAM at startup is AFAIK at a random state, so you can just leave a part of RAM untouched and use mathematical methods to derive those random bits to numbers of a certain length, much like a Mersenne Twister.</div>

